appears on the ballot alongside the delegatecandidates said 
steve copple jesse jacksons national delegate coordinator the 
bulk of the people are going to vote for their presidential 
candidates supporters 
illinois delegate selection system is a handicap for jackson 
whose stronghold is three predominantly black districts in chicago 
those districts will elect 24 of the 113 democratic delegates but 
his chances of success elsewhere are questionable 
simons other democratic foes had little success in recruiting 
