between 6 million and 8 million wilson charges ehrlich was 
mario biaggis partner in the plunder of wedtech when he got it 
he split it wilson charged 
richard biaggi became a lawyer in 1982 and became the front 
man in this case wilson said sometimes taking money or stock in 
his fathers name betso was a smaller player who took stock 
options in his name for his friend neglia wilson alleged 
wilson said he would present testimony from wedtech accountants 
