money about 16 million to some 40 projects it says about 2000 
applications have come from both catholics and protestants despite 
paisleys call for a boycott and hopes to have distributed the 
whole amount within 18 months 
i would have liked to see quicker progress but im 
absolutely certain if we plunged in spending money like drunken 
sailors it would have been disastrous said charles eb brett 
the lawyer and former public official who chairs the funds 
sevenmember board 
