art of baksheesh the arabic word for petty bribery 
but the advice doesnt just center on money the article advises 
that a pack of cigarettes may convince a taxi driver in angola to 
get you to the airport and a bottle of liquor or contact points for 
a 57 chevy can get you just about anything in burma 
also included is a section where worldweary travelers pass on 
tips to surviving off the beaten path 
these include suggestions to carry a golf ball in your luggage 
because many of the worlds hotels dont have drain plugs and to 
