hardware stores jumped a sharp 23 percent 
sales at furniture and appliance stores were up 03 percent in 
february following an even stronger 27 percent january increase 
sales at specialty clothing stores climbed 06 percent in 
february only a partial rebound following a giant 33 percent 
january decline 
sales at gasoline stations fell 16 percent in february while 
