payments are part of a restructuring plan aimed at thwarting a 
hostile takeover bid from henley of la jolla calif 
henley had filed a lawsuit seeking an injunction to block 
issuance of the debentures 
the lawsuit also asked the court to declare santa fes recently 
enacted shareholderrights plan invalid to rescind the appointment 
of two olympia amp york executives to the santa fe board and to 
allow henley to propose an amendment that would make it possible 
for henley to elect a majority of directors at the santa fes 
annual meeting may 24 
